00:14.710 --> 00:16.886
[suspenseful music]

00:16.929 --> 00:19.106
- Between you and me,
Mr. Shine,

00:19.149 --> 00:21.369
the man is a few peas short
of a casserole.

00:21.412 --> 00:24.372
- Let's go ahead
and kill the idiot.

00:24.415 --> 00:26.069
- This is not gonna
end well for you.

00:26.113 --> 00:28.071
- Don't cause a scene, Sax.
- No.

00:28.115 --> 00:31.074
- Think of all the children,
especially yours.

00:31.118 --> 00:33.076
I'm just happy that you're
finally hearing the truth.

00:33.120 --> 00:35.426
It's about time someone final--
- What's that supposed to mean?

00:35.470 --> 00:36.906
- Your father lied
to your mother

00:36.949 --> 00:38.255
and then ran out on her.

00:38.299 --> 00:40.127
And then your mother lied
to your father about you

00:40.170 --> 00:42.825
and then to you
about your father.

00:42.868 --> 00:44.348
- From the lady.

00:44.392 --> 00:45.915
♪

00:45.958 --> 00:48.091
- Here comes the fun.

00:48.135 --> 00:50.224
Are you ready?
- [gulps]

00:50.267 --> 00:53.096
- [distorted voice]
Do you know what bugs crave?

00:53.140 --> 00:55.098
Darkness.
The shadows.

00:55.142 --> 00:57.492
- Amanda?
- Nick.

00:57.535 --> 01:00.147
- There's something living
in your mind, Blue.

01:00.190 --> 01:01.757
[distorted screaming]

01:01.800 --> 01:04.368
- Orcus, God of Death.

01:04.412 --> 01:08.459
With Isabella dead,
you will have no escape.

01:08.503 --> 01:09.852
[hollers]

01:09.895 --> 01:13.986
- So let me get this right--
you want me to kill you?

01:14.030 --> 01:16.946
- If--if I die, he dies.

01:16.989 --> 01:18.774
- What the hell?

01:18.817 --> 01:21.777
[indistinct shouting]

01:21.820 --> 01:24.519
- I love you.
[both screaming]

01:27.043 --> 01:30.046
[moving operatic music]

01:30.090 --> 01:33.049
[women vocalizing]

01:33.093 --> 01:35.791
♪

01:35.834 --> 01:37.967
- [laughs]

01:38.010 --> 01:39.664
Heaven!

01:39.708 --> 01:46.671
♪

01:46.715 --> 01:50.632
[cows mooing]

01:50.675 --> 01:53.504
[door opens, creaks]

01:58.422 --> 02:00.294
Oh...

02:00.337 --> 02:03.471
[banjo playing]

02:03.514 --> 02:06.735
♪

02:06.778 --> 02:10.217
