02:17.659 --> 02:19.835
Men have offered me
their wives.

02:19.878 --> 02:22.838
Men have offered me the eyes

02:22.881 --> 02:25.841
of their most-loved child.

02:25.884 --> 02:28.235
But you, you went out

02:28.278 --> 02:31.194
