02:31.238 --> 02:33.805
Well done, Scaramucci.

02:33.849 --> 02:35.242
Well done.

02:35.285 --> 02:38.636
- So you're not gonna
torture me for all of eternity?

02:38.680 --> 02:41.639
- No, no, I've got to get
back upstairs, you know?

02:41.683 --> 02:43.946
♪

02:43.989 --> 02:45.861
- But we're dead.

02:45.904 --> 02:48.080
- Oh, Blue, you silly man.

02:48.124 --> 02:51.040
