03:29.426 --> 03:32.255
- Honey, you're home.

03:32.299 --> 03:34.257
[eerie music]

03:34.301 --> 03:37.826
- Oh, my God.

03:37.869 --> 03:39.610
[gags]

03:39.654 --> 03:40.394
- [whines]

03:40.437 --> 03:43.092
- Oh, no.
Whiskers.

03:43.135 --> 03:44.876
♪

03:44.920 --> 03:46.965
