03:47.009 --> 03:49.968
[spoon clatters lightly]

03:50.012 --> 03:54.103
♪

03:54.146 --> 03:57.062
- Welcome home, boo.

03:57.106 --> 03:58.542
- [sobs]

03:58.586 --> 04:01.197
- We've been waiting for you.

04:01.241 --> 04:04.766
- [screaming]

04:04.809 --> 04:07.159
[overlapping chatter]

04:07.203 --> 04:09.031
- Amanda?

04:09.074 --> 04:10.772
- Nick.

04:10.815 --> 04:12.774
- What the fuck
are you doing here?

04:12.817 --> 04:14.297
