04:37.364 --> 04:40.062
- Life and love.

04:40.105 --> 04:42.151
- Molly.

04:42.194 --> 04:44.893
What did Sonny Shine do to you?

04:44.936 --> 04:47.330
- It's good for the baby.

04:47.374 --> 04:50.115
- Uh--okay, enough.

04:50.159 --> 04:51.247
