04:54.990 --> 04:57.122
- I'm pregnant.

04:57.166 --> 04:58.559
♪

04:58.602 --> 05:01.126
- Who's the father?
- I don't know!

05:01.170 --> 05:03.477
♪

05:03.520 --> 05:05.174
- [crowd on TV]
Five, four, three...

05:05.217 --> 05:06.697
- Is it safe
to come out yet?

05:06.741 --> 05:08.656
- [sighs]
- That was quick.

05:08.699 --> 05:11.354
- Consider it a compliment.

05:11.398 --> 05:12.747
- [on TV]
Happy New Year!

05:12.790 --> 05:16.228
- [distorted voice]
Well, well, well, Nick Sax.

05:16.272 --> 05:17.795
The stork is bringing us

05:17.839 --> 05:20.363
a beautiful, bouncing
special something.

05:20.407 --> 05:23.801
This is a blessed moment
for all of us.

05:23.845 --> 05:27.065
♪

05:27.109 --> 05:29.198
For mostly me.

05:29.241 --> 05:31.200
- [growling]

05:31.243 --> 05:33.158
♪

05:33.202 --> 05:36.423
Hey, get out
of the fucking way.

05:36.466 --> 05:40.644
- [laughing wickedly]

05:40.688 --> 05:46.389
♪

05:46.433 --> 05:48.826
