the "aw, shucks" routine.

07:28.970 --> 07:33.975
This thing keeps
those furry fucks in line.

07:34.018 --> 07:35.629
[laughs, coughs]

07:35.672 --> 07:38.109
- Can I see you tonight
or tomorrow?

07:38.153 --> 07:39.110
- Mm...

07:39.154 --> 07:40.285
- Maybe this weekend?
- Well...

07:40.329 --> 07:42.157
- What does your
Memorial Day look like?

07:42.200 --> 07:43.419
- [sighs]

07:43.463 --> 07:45.465
You're as green as a frog

07:45.508 --> 07:47.554
with chlamydia, aren't you?

07:47.597 --> 07:51.166
- Well, it's just--
last night was so special.

07:51.209 --> 07:54.169
- It was...fine.

07:54.212 --> 07:56.127
You're a sweet kid, Happy.

07:56.171 --> 07:58.086
I'll give you a call.

08:00.044 --> 08:03.439
[upbeat jazzy music]

08:03.483 --> 08:07.487
- It's so white in here.

08:07.530 --> 08:10.838
