09:35.139 --> 09:36.663
Well, I did.

09:36.706 --> 09:39.404
- Well, whoop-dee-fucking-do
for you.

09:39.448 --> 09:41.755
While you were out fornicating

09:41.798 --> 09:43.974
with what I hope
is another imaginary friend

09:44.018 --> 09:46.934
and not a mouse
or a pineapple or something,

09:46.977 --> 09:50.154
I had a psychotropic breakdown,
went to an orgy,

09:50.198 --> 09:54.158
uh, found out Smoothie's alive,
working for Sonny Shine,

09:54.202 --> 09:56.900
and kidnapped a Wishee.

09:56.944 --> 09:58.423
