10:26.364 --> 10:28.279
- Having a daydream.

10:28.323 --> 10:29.367
- Okay.

10:29.411 --> 10:31.979
- That this was our home...

10:32.022 --> 10:34.155
together.

10:34.198 --> 10:37.680
Nick and Amanda.

10:37.724 --> 10:40.248
