- Huh?

11:35.999 --> 11:38.262
Nothing.
Nothing, nothing, nothing.

11:38.306 --> 11:40.743
[stammering] Why aren't you
at, uh, uh, Grandma's?

11:40.787 --> 11:43.354
- She fell asleep.
- I'm so glad you're here.

11:43.398 --> 11:44.921
I missed you so much.

11:44.965 --> 11:46.749
- [whispering] Hey, hey, let's
not mention the pregnancy.

11:46.793 --> 11:48.882
- Our little secret.
- Yeah.

11:48.925 --> 11:52.233
- Guess who's gonna be
a big sister?

11:52.276 --> 11:55.062
