of Orcus.

14:07.934 --> 14:09.544
- Fucking Wishees.

14:09.587 --> 14:11.807
- Idols have risen up,

14:11.851 --> 14:13.374
and just
when their light seems

14:13.417 --> 14:15.506
to shine the brightest...
[gunshot]

14:15.550 --> 14:16.725
Each...

14:16.768 --> 14:17.726
[screaming, metal crashing]

14:17.769 --> 14:19.902
