to bring joy to the world.

14:29.869 --> 14:31.522
- Sonny Shine!

14:31.566 --> 14:36.049
- And on Easter Day,
the pattern will repeat.

14:36.092 --> 14:39.574
The idol will be
struck down tragically...

14:39.617 --> 14:42.664
in the eyes of millions.

14:46.973 --> 14:49.279
- The God of Death is gonna
kill Sonny Shine

14:49.323 --> 14:50.585
on national TV.

14:50.628 --> 14:54.284
